dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Washburn_Hydro_2018.gdb'. The features included in this geodatabase are 'Washburn_Hydro_2018_Line' and 'Washburn_Hydro_2018_Poly'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
